<h1>Feedback Requested</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

<p>The interview with <strong><%= @candidate.full_name %></strong> for the <strong><%= @job.title %></strong> position has been completed.</p>

<p>Please submit your feedback and scorecard at your earliest convenience to help the hiring team make an informed decision.</p>

<h2>Interview Summary</h2>

<table style="border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 8px 16px 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">Candidate:</td>
    <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><%= @candidate.full_name %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 8px 16px 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">Position:</td>
    <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><%= @job.title %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 8px 16px 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">Interview Type:</td>
    <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><%= @interview.interview_type_label %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 8px 16px 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">Date:</td>
    <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><%= @interview.scheduled_at_formatted(format: :date) %></td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p>Your feedback is valuable in evaluating candidates fairly and consistently.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
<%= @organization.name %> Recruiting</p>
